00:44:58.680 --> 00:45:03.240
 by supplementing retinacillin or cortisol.

00:45:03.240 --> 00:45:11.200
 But in the case of progesterone, if you are feeding blood supply

00:45:11.200 --> 00:45:14.000
 to an ovary, for example, measuring

00:45:14.000 --> 00:45:17.160
 how much progesterone is synthesizing,

00:45:17.160 --> 00:45:23.560
