00:45:32.240 --> 00:45:38.080
 The more progesterone is given, no one

00:45:38.080 --> 00:45:40.240
 knows exactly what the limits are.

00:45:40.240 --> 00:45:43.240
 But there's a positive feedback relationship.

00:45:43.240 --> 00:45:50.440
 So an example, the most vivid thing that I've seen

00:45:50.440 --> 00:45:53.840
 was a woman who, since puberty--

00:45:53.840 --> 00:45:59.200
