 are certain endocrine hormones made in the skin?

00:48:12.840 --> 00:48:17.360
 Yeah, in 1960, someone was studying tonsils

00:48:17.360 --> 00:48:22.680
 and found that insulin could be identified in the tonsils.

00:48:22.680 --> 00:48:25.520
 And people just hadn't been looking.

00:48:25.520 --> 00:48:31.680
