00:48:34.520 --> 00:48:38.000
 can produce the pituitary hormones that

00:48:38.000 --> 00:48:42.920
 activate the production of things

00:48:42.920 --> 00:48:47.840
 such as cortisol, androgens, progesterone.

00:48:47.840 --> 00:48:55.840
 The skin is possibly our biggest steroid-producing organ.

00:48:55.840 --> 00:48:58.880
 But it's almost always ignored.

00:48:58.880 --> 00:49:03.480
 The brain is another major steroid-producing organ.

00:49:03.480 --> 00:49:09.240
